<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Şifre Güncelleme Başarılı</title>
  <style>
    /* Genel Stil */
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6A11CB, #2575FC);
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
    }

    /* Kart Tasarımı */
    .success-container {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 15px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      width: 90%;
      max-width: 400px;
    }

    .success-container h1 {
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .success-container p {
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .success-container button {
      background: white;
      color: #2575FC;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: bold;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
    }

    .success-container button:hover {
      background: #2575FC;
      color: white;
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    .success-icon {
      font-size: 50px;
      color: white;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      animation: pop-in 0.5s ease-out;
    }

    @keyframes pop-in {
      0% {
        transform: scale(0.5);
        opacity: 0;
      }
      100% {
        transform: scale(1);
        opacity: 1;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="success-container">
    <div class="success-icon">✔</div>
    <h1>Şifre Güncelleme Başarılı!</h1>
    <p>Şifreniz başarıyla güncellendi. Artık yeni şifrenizle giriş yapabilirsiniz.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
